text: Farley Hill may be a reference to: *Farley Hill, Saint Peter, Barbados, currently a national park in the parish of Saint Peter, Barbados *Farley Hill, Luton, a ward and suburb in south Luton, Bedfordshire, England *Farley Hill, Berkshire, a village in Berkshire, England ==See also== * Farley (disambiguation) * Farley Hall (disambiguation) * Farley Hills, a mountain range in Baker County, Oregon * Farnley Hall (disambiguation)
title: Farley Hill
